  <text x="355" y="190" fill="#1b1a18" font-family="Apple SD Gothic Neo, Noto Sans KR, sans-serif" font-size="14" font-weight="600">애플 (AAPL)</text>
  <text x="355" y="207" fill="#6b6b63" font-family="Apple SD Gothic Neo, Noto Sans KR, sans-serif" font-size="11">50주 × $180 × 1,350 = ₩12,150,000</text>
  <text x="720" y="190" fill="#1b1a18" font-family="Apple SD Gothic Neo, Noto Sans KR, sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" text-anchor="end">60%</text>
  
