  <text x="355" y="255" fill="#1b1a18" font-family="Apple SD Gothic Neo, Noto Sans KR, sans-serif" font-size="14" font-weight="600">TIGER S&P500 (360750)</text>
  <text x="355" y="272" fill="#6b6b63" font-family="Apple SD Gothic Neo, Noto Sans KR, sans-serif" font-size="11">10주 × ₩1,350,000 = ₩13,500,000</text>
  <text x="720" y="255" fill="#1b1a18" font-family="Apple SD Gothic Neo, Noto Sans KR, sans-serif" font-size="12" font-weight="700" text-anchor="end">5%</text>
  
  <!-- Title -->
  <text x="60" y="70" fill="#1b1a18" font-family="Apple SD Gothic Neo, Noto Sans KR, sans-serif" font-size="28" font-weight="700">보유 종목 계산기</text>
  <text x="60" y="90" fill="#6b6b63" font-family="Apple SD Gothic Neo, Noto Sans KR, sans-serif" font-size="14">무료 포트폴리오 관리 및 실시간 주식 가격 조회</text>
  
